Definition:
Custom GPTs are specialized versions of ChatGPT that you can create for your team or organization.
They combine instructions, tone, and tools (APIs, files, connectors) to behave like a role-specific AI assistant.

Purpose:
To tailor ChatGPTâ€™s behavior, personality, and capabilities to your business workflows â€” without writing code.


